{
  "stem": "16163.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He would bring us food, and he will be in contact with somebody in Vlotho.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when everything is over, he would make sure that we get transportation back to Vlotho.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that this way my father didn't get arrested because everybody else got arrested.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Gunter's father got arrested, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "On Kristallnacht?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On Kristallnacht-- all the men, most of them went.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was on the 10th of November, 1938.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were hiding out in this office there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the next day, I don't remember exactly, but I believe there was some kind of a car that they took us back to Vlotho, and life continued.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no schools after that and no work for anybody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was just a waiting period of time till 1942.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A lot of people tried to get out from Germany still.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They went to Holland, not that it helped them very much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sometimes, like I mentioned, that one family who moved to Hanover.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And some other people tried to get to Hanover and made it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But none of them came back anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They all were arrested way ahead of us and sent away and didn't return.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that's the story till [LAUGHS] 1938.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From '38 to '42 just time--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to go to work in Herford-- I remember that-- after the Jewish school was over, because the Jewish school only started in '39 to '40.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in '40-- in '41 to-- I worked in Herford.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to go to work because there were a law that old Jewish girls who had no school-- no more school or anything, had to work and were sent to Berlin at the time.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know if you ever heard of that, the [?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
